title: Why Social Media SUCKED In 2020!
description:
In this episode Jessi and Stew talk about the shift social media took in 2020. The world has been crazy this past year and people online were feelin' it! Cyber bullying and judging others were at an all time high. Do you agree?! Listen to this episode to hear their take on it and listen to the experiences they had with this topic in 2020.
